review_data: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2023
name: V2KRVW
title: Fancy sticks!
review: "These are some nice fancy sticks compared to the twigs we used before!" Words from a 9-y/o while roasting smores over a campfire. Very sturdy, easy to use, and love the safety provided by the extendable feature & the tip caps. Nice carrying bag. The only downside is once I removed the grips to wash them, I couldn't get them all the way back on afterwards, as if the rubber shrank a little bit. And no, they weren't in the dishwasher.
